briefTitle: Comparison of CHS-0214 to Enbrel (Etanercept) in Patients With Chronic Plaque Psoriasis (PsO)
officialTitle: A Double-Blind, Randomized, Parallel-Group, Active-Control Study to Compare the Efficacy and Safety of CHS-0214 Versus Enbrel in Subjects With Chronic Plaque Psoriasis (RaPsOdy)
summary: This is a two part study comparing CHS-0214 to Enbrel in patients with chronic plaque PsO who have not yet received any biologic therapy for any indication (other than insulin or hormones).

primaryOutcome.measure: Proportion of Subjects Achieving PASI-75(75% Improvement in Psoriasis Area and Severity Index) From Baseline at Week 12
